              code testing some code

            aside
              h3 Disabling buttons
              p.tight
                | Note that buttons disabled via the 
                code btn-disabled
                |  class are only visually disabled. You should always opt to disable buttons via the 
                code disabled
                |  attribute to ensure they are functionally disabled.

